{"tid":2231422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Stephy鄧麗欣算唔算二十一世紀最具代表性的香港美少女？","createTime":"2020-10-05T15:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T16:19:50.000Z","uid":38539,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5ed4b6d6e71df836d765c269a1ec5907f2d734","tid":2231422,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pujipwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPujipwm.jpg&h=15f702e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3TGnh1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3TGnh1.jpg&h=5f2372e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStephy無論外貌和氣質都係極屈機，係當世數一數二的絕頂靚女之一，<br />\n個時嘅佢就係香港美女的標準，啲o靚妹仔瘋狂跟佢嘅衣著風格，<br />\n而且佢當年啲歌係極具標誌性，幾乎成為現今80,90後香港人的共同回憶。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gAtoStcrKVU&amp;ab_channel=TimelessMusicHongKong%E5%A4%A9%E7%A2%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgAtoStcrKVU%26ab_channel%3DTimelessMusicHongKong%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%25A2%259F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=2ac84a4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gAtoStcrKVU&amp;ab_channel=TimelessMusicHongKong%E5%A4%A9%E7%A2%9F</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IsHaWo1-0xc&amp;ab_channel=TimelessMusicHongKong%E5%A4%A9%E7%A2%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIsHaWo1-0xc%26ab_channel%3DTimelessMusicHongKong%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%25A2%259F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=fbe802cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IsHaWo1-0xc&amp;ab_channel=TimelessMusicHongKong%E5%A4%A9%E7%A2%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n我記得個時為咗儲佢堆YES卡，有一排每逢放學、放假瞞住屋企人偷偷出去做童工送外賣，15蚊一個鐘、一個月都有千零蚊，用哂買佢啲YES卡，然後收埋係餅盒放落床底，有一日返到屋企發現老母執屋掉撚咗我罐餅盒，即刻喊住咁衝去垃圾房搵Stephy，仲要搵唔到喊足七日七夜，最後陪我走出呢段陰影嘅係GEM同佢首Get Over You。"},{"pid":"3257dc9e97a08c53d54a5b0fa3b48ee6e087c0e4","t